# Our~products and services

LUWRAIN is a platform for the creation of apps for the blind and partially-sighted.
It provides the~access to~information resources and network services.
LUWRAIN is~free and [published under the~terms of~the~GNU~Public License v.~3](local:/doc/legal/).
Our~distributions do~not require any~additional software or other accessibility technologies to~be~installed on~your computer.
LUWRAIN can be~launched on~Microsoft Windows, GNU/Linux or as~a~standalone operating system on~the~Linux kernel.

* [LUWRAIN for~Microsoft Windows](local:/download/windows/)
* [LUWRAIN for~GNU/Linux](local:/download/linux/)
* [LUWRAIN as~an~ISO~image](local:/download/iso/)

[...all resources for~download, including unstable distributions, the~source code and the~materials of~our~partners.](local:/download/)

## LUWRAIN~Books

[LUWRAIN~Books (books.luwrain.org)](local:https://books.luwrain.org) is a~cloud service for~the~creation and storing of audiobooks.
It~is~a~perfect tool for~publishers, libraries  and literature lovers.
The~features of~LUWRAIN Books includes  tools for~processing of~source materials,
linguistic annotation,
delivering of~created books to readers
and a~support of~the~DAISY format for~the~blind.

